original_title: The Shoji Tabuchi Show! Vol. IV
overview: Shoji and Dorthy Tabuchi, along with their daughter Christina Lingo-Tabuchi, present their sparkling family variety show live from Branson, Missouri! Memories are made of these ... the sights and sounds of the wonderful show that's the talk of Branson!
title: The Shoji Tabuchi Show! Vol. IV
